				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Can the King/Queen/Prince be single pet pulled in Chardok?
<br />
I was reading another post about pet pulling and saw Ronaan (I think) mention this.  I'm new to the necro class and am not sure if this would work.
<br />
Can the Royals be pulled to the entrance? If a Non-KOS or SOS rogue can get to the royals to target them can you assist off of him to send your pet in to attack and pull back to you? Will you need the rogue to open doors for the pet or not? Will you need the /pet hold AA to do this succesfully? If they can't be pulled to entrance do you need to get your force inside the locked doors via normal raid or COH mage?
<br />
If there is anything else that I missed or information that anyone can supply please respond.
<br />
My main is a 62 Cleric that is stuck here on his epic and I have started to 2-box a mage and necro with a buddy of mine as a rogue just to be able to finish my epic as my family style guild has all but fallen apart.
<br />
I'm sure i'll start posting in the newbie section soon as well as I have very limited experience with casters and pet classes lol and now i'm gonna 2-box them. Ought to be fun and I've found a wealth of knowledge on this board already.
<br />

<br />
Tahnks,
