				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I use to trio the king with another necro and rogue. Myself and the other necro were both non-kos and would heal the 49 pet while we brought the king up too the zone in. He does hit fairly hard and quick so the pet will die in no time if it stays in his melee range too long with only 1 person healing.
<br />

<br />
Other times when I had 40 minutes or so too spare, i'd get my cleric and myself summoned into the royals and just kill the king in the hallway by the second locked door. This way was tougher for me because of my gear and the amount of roamers that need to be killed. Much funner alternative though.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=516627" target="_blank" class="postlink">Karnagee</a>
<br />
